‐Right there!

78
00:04:24,931 --> 00:04:26,057
Well, what have we here?

79
00:04:26,057 --> 00:04:27,976
Look, Jigen, it's our
friends from the media.

80
00:04:27,976 --> 00:04:29,895
Tell me, what newsworthy
thing have we been

81
00:04:29,895 --> 00:04:31,062
accused of today?

82
00:04:31,062 --> 00:04:32,731
(grunts)

83
00:04:34,483 --> 00:04:35,650
Man, that hurts.

84
00:04:35,650 --> 00:04:37,402
Didn't you say you'd
stayed here before?

85
00:04:37,402 --> 00:04:38,820
