downhill, hasn't it?

88
00:04:42,491 --> 00:04:44,284
Oh, gee, you think?

89
00:04:44,284 --> 00:04:45,869
You really gotta
get out more, Jigen.

90
00:04:45,869 --> 00:04:49,039
Mr. Lupin, I have
great news for you.

91
00:04:49,039 --> 00:04:50,582
You and your friends
will be breaking

92
00:04:50,582 --> 00:04:53,418
into Tiffany & Company
this Christmas Eve.

93
00:04:53,418 --> 00:04:54,377
Huh?

94
00:04:54,377 --> 00:04:55,378
