116
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:45,220
I picked this room
just for you.

117
00:05:45,220 --> 00:05:47,639
I hope it meets
your requirements.

118
00:05:47,639 --> 00:05:49,349
Huh.

119
00:05:49,349 --> 00:05:57,649
♪

120
00:05:57,649 --> 00:06:00,443
Wow, I've been in
a lot of great hotels,

121
00:06:00,443 --> 00:06:02,696
but this room is in
a class all its own.

122
00:06:02,696 --> 00:06:05,991
