155
00:07:18,438 --> 00:07:20,148
♪

156
00:07:20,148 --> 00:07:23,026
Yeah, a nice long holiday
in prison is a downside.

157
00:07:23,026 --> 00:07:24,527
I don't like it.

158
00:07:24,527 --> 00:07:25,612
Hey, we gotta get going.

159
00:07:25,612 --> 00:07:27,405
We're gonna miss
that flight to Panama.

160
00:07:27,405 --> 00:07:30,533
♪

161
00:07:30,533 --> 00:07:31,868
Where's he going?

162
00:07:31,868 --> 00:07:33,286
Forget it, it's fishing.

163
00:07:33,286 --> 00:07:36,331
Nothing could stop
him from that.

164
00:07:36,331 --> 00:07:37,666
I see this all the time.

165
00:07:37,666 --> 00:07:39,334
Rich people like you
always make the mistake

166
00:07:39,334 --> 00:07:40,960
of assuming the rest
of the world is as

167
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:42,754
motivated by money as you are.

168
00:07:42,754 --> 00:07:45,757
Too bad, it was a cute
idea for a special.

169
00:07:45,757 --> 00:07:48,510
I would've watched it,
but it's not to be.

170
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:49,594
Guess not.

171
00:07:49,594 --> 00:07:51,429
What the hell,
long as I'm here,

172
00:07:51,429 --> 00:07:53,473
I guess I might
as well stay a while.

173
00:07:53,473 --> 00:07:55,892
I'm not sure that's
such a great idea.

174
00:07:55,892 --> 00:07:57,185
Oh, and why not?

175
00:07:57,185 --> 00:08:00,480
Wouldn't everyone
mistake you for a hooker?

176
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,691
Well, it's been a pleasure.

177
00:08:06,903 --> 00:08:08,154
Ugh!

178
00:08:08,154 --> 00:08:09,698
(groans)

179
00:08:09,698 --> 00:08:11,825
