184
00:08:21,376 --> 00:08:23,628
It was a perfect opportunity!

185
00:08:23,628 --> 00:08:25,797
Arresting Lupin on television!

186
00:08:25,797 --> 00:08:27,674
In primetime!

187
00:08:27,674 --> 00:08:29,300
Look, it's Fujiko.

188
00:08:29,300 --> 00:08:30,301
Huh?

189
00:08:41,938 --> 00:08:43,815
Have you ever spent
the holiday season

190
00:08:43,815 --> 00:08:44,816
here in New York?

191
