It's really quite lovely.

192
00:08:46,317 --> 00:08:47,485
Huh?

193
00:08:52,157 --> 00:08:54,409
Well, welcome.

194
00:08:54,409 --> 00:08:55,910
So, did you have
any luck finding

195
00:08:55,910 --> 00:08:57,287
a more suitable hotel?

196
00:08:57,287 --> 00:08:58,621
